sures the relative buying and selling pressure on a stock based on the value of trades made on an uptick in price and the value of trades made on a downtick in price the updown ratio is calculated by dividing the value of uptick trades by the value of downtick trades net money flow is the value of uptick trades minus the value of downtick trades our calculations are based on comprehensive delayed quotes stock money flow na advertisement competitors elrnf company change pe ttm bbox black box corp    rmbs rambus inc    idti integrated device technology inc    mzor mazor robotics ltd adr    more information on elrnf competitor data provided by capital cube profile elrnf elron electronic industries ltd engages in one business segment  holdings and activities of the companys headquarters this segment includes headquarters of the company and reflects the investing activity in investee companies and their sale the company was founded the triangle tower tel aviv ta  israel email website map employees  sector diversified holding companies sales or revenue  industry businessconsumer services y sales change  fiscal year ends december  download reports eduardo sergio elsztain chairman ari bronshtein chief executive officer yaron elad chief financial officer  vice president zvika slovin vice presidentmedical  life sciences more research  ratings elron electronic industries ltdelrnf pershare earnings actuals and estimates quarterly annual elrnf will report fy  earnings on false elrnf will report q earnings on false actual analyst range consensus na na na na na na     na na na na q  estimate trends current   month ago   months ago  q  estimate trends current   month ago   months ago  fy  estimate trends current   month ago   months ago  fy  estimate trends current   month ago   months ago  more financials elron electronic industries ltdelrnf quarterly annual net income   m m m m mar  jun  sep  dec  mar   b  b      mar  quarter trend net income growth  sales or revenue  sales or re