d topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsinvestment management  fund operators overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse elrnta on tel aviv stock exchange ila  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description elron electronic industries ltd elron incorporated on october   is an operational holding company that focuses on building technology companies mainly in the field of medical devices its group companies include companies at various stages of development and business maturation operating in various technology fields such as medical device and other fields the company is involved in the management of its group companies by means of membership and providing assistance to management the company operates through holdings and corporate operations segment the company is engaged in matters of policy guidance strategic planning marketing selecting and manning senior management positions determining the business plan approving investments and budgets development and operational guidance assistance in creating strategic partnerships and the overall ongoing monitoring of its group companies performance its subsidiaries include elbit ltd elbit dep technology holdings ltd dep rdc rafael development corporation ltd rdc and rd seed ltd rdseedthe companys main group companies include brainsgate ltd brainsgate pocared diagnostics ltd pocared and rdc brainsgate is engaged in developing an invasive platform for the treatment of central nervous system cns diseases pocared is engaged in developing a realtime and automated laboratory system for infectious diseases diagnosis pocareds diagnostic system uses optical technology and an algorithm for data analysis the system is designed for use by microbiological laboratories and hospitals as an alternative to the current microbiological diagnostic method of growing pathogen cultures rdc seeks to identify technological projects and invest in companies in diverse fields that will either commercialize rafaels military technologies in the civilian market or which will be benefited by rafaels technology and knowhow following identification of such projects rdc develops the relevant technologies and in the case of military technologies adapts them for commercial use initially by utilizing its own management and funding resources thereafter by spinning off activities into independent companies and at later stages from external funding rdc owns rdseedrdseed is a holding company which invests in earlystage companies in cyber information technology and enterprise software rdseeds main holdings include cloudyn software ltd cloudyn open legacy technologies ltd open legacy and ironscales ltd ironscales cloudyn is engaged in the development and marketing of a platform for the optimization of cloud service resources open legacy is developing an open standards based software platform for delivering core enterprise applications legacy and onpremise as digital services such as digital banking ironscales provides a cloudbased softwareasaservice saas solution which aims to train the employees of an organization take an active part in identifying and preventing targeted email attacks spearphishingthe companys other group companies include aqwisewise water technologies ltd aqwise atlantium technologies ltd atlantium notal vision inc notal vision cartiheal  ltd cartiheal coramaze technologies gmbh coramaze and plymedia israel  ltd aqwise develops manufactures and provides biological water and wastewater treatment solutions for the industrial and municipal markets atlantium develops manufactures and provides ultravioletbased water disinfection solutions notal vision is engaged in the development manufacturing and marketing of systems and services for remote monitoring of agerelated macular degeneration amd patients cartiheal is developing an implant for repairing cartilage and osteochondral defects in loadbearing joints such as the knee coramaze is developing a minimally invasive device for the treatment of functional mitral valve regurgitation reverse flow in the left side of the heart due to the expansion of the left ventricle that prevents the complete closure of the mitral valve plymedia israel  ltd is engaged in the development and marketing of advertising exchange services » full overview of elrnta company address elron electronic industries ltd  azrieli centerthe triangular tower nd floortel avivyafo      p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation ari bronshtein  niv levy  yaron elad  doron cohen  eduardo elsztain  » more officers  directors elron electronic industries ltd news briefmicrosoft israel research and development signs deal with cloudyn software jun   » more elrnta news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsinvestment management  fund operators